Source: pg-flight-recorder
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), gawk
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/dventimisupabase/pg_flight_recorder

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-flight-recorder
Architecture: all
Provides: postgresql-pg-flight-recorder
Depends: postgresql-PGVERSION, postgresql-PGVERSION-cron, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Server-side PostgreSQL performance flight recorder
 pg_flight_recorder captures performance telemetry through pg_cron and ships
 the pgfr_record collector plus pgfr_analyze reporting extension.
